text: Jaime Hernández González (born 18 September 1953) is a Mexican politician from the Institutional Revolutionary Party. From 2000 to 2003 he served as Deputy of the LVIII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Jalisco. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Guadalajara, Jalisco Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Institutional Revolutionary Party politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
